1. Switch in git to the dev branch and pull the recent changes.
2. Create a new branch based on the dev branch with the prefix and name.
3. Begin with the implementation.
4. Check for linting errors for PHP, CSS and JavaScript.
5. Create unit/function tests for PHP and JavaScript.
6. Run the tests and adjust them if they fail. Repeat this until all tests are passed.
7. Create a changelog to record the implementation. Use always the current date. You can search the web for the current date.